---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact Nichole at Wellness Savings" description="Get in touch with Nichole. Have a wellness deal tip, product suggestion, or question? I'd love to hear from you.">
  <div class="container-narrow about-section">
    <h1>Contact Me</h1>
    <p>I'd love to hear from you! Whether you have a deal tip, a product you'd like me to review, a question about a discount code, or just want to say hi — drop me a message.</p>

    <div style="background:var(--color-badge-bg);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius-md);padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;">
      <h2 style="margin-top:0;">Email Me Directly</h2>
      <p style="font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">📧 <a href="mailto:hello@wellnesssavings.org" style="font-weight:600;">hello@wellnesssavings.org</a></p>
      <p style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);">I typically respond within 24-48 hours.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>What to Contact Me About</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Deal tips:</strong> Found a great wellness deal? Share it with the community!</li>
      <li><strong>Product reviews:</strong> Want me to review a specific product? Let me know.</li>
      <li><strong>Brand partnerships:</strong> Interested in featuring your product on Wellness Savings? I'd love to chat.</li>
      <li><strong>Questions:</strong> Have a question about a discount code or article? I'm here to help.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Connect With Me</h2>
    <p>Follow Wellness Savings for the latest deals and wellness tips:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Email newsletter:</strong> <a href="/newsletter/">Sign up here</a> for weekly deal alerts</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="disclosure" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">
      <strong>Note:</strong> I personally read every message. Your privacy matters to me — I'll never share your email or contact information with third parties.
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>